櫶字的基本解释

櫶
xiǎn
〔櫶木〕即蚬木，一种常绿乔木，木材坚实，可供建筑和造船用。

櫶字的汉语字典释义

[①]［xiǎn］
櫶木。即蚬木。常绿乔木。单叶互生，椭圆状卵形，花单性，白色，蒴果椭圆形。木材坚实细致，可供建筑及制船舰、机械等用。为我国珍贵用材树种之一。

Chinese dictionary definition of words
[①]［xiǎn］
櫶木. Namely Clam Wood. Evergreen trees. The leaves are alternate, elliptic-ovate, the flowers are unisexual, white, and the capsules are elliptic. The wood is solid and meticulous, and can be used for construction, shipbuilding, machinery, etc. It is one of the precious timber species in our country.
